Package org.harctoolbox.irp

Class Duration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.harctoolbox.irp.IrpObject
      • org.harctoolbox.irp.Duration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Floatable, IrStreamItem, XmlExport
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Extent, Flash, Gap
    public abstract class Duration
extends IrpObject
implements IrStreamItem, Floatable
    This class implements Durations in Chapter 3 and 4. Depends on its Protocol (GeneralSpec and NameEngine), except for this, it is immutable.
